{"tid":782924,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"主題：今日最爆！高登仔有專用手提電話！仲要好平，好靚好鬼正！","createTime":"2018-08-17T07:08:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-06T08:46:26.000Z","uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"4602c66fd0fb43da601590fbd5c2fd2179af3d53","tid":782924,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T07:08:18.000Z","msg":"一般嚟講，只要你係高登討論區會員，你就可以自稱為「高登仔」。不過，你有無上高登，其實無人知，但而家只要有「佢」，你就可以 show 埋俾人知，我係高登仔....<br />\n<br />\n原來，高登即日做埋手機代理加網絡商！推出全港首部有高登仔 Logo 嘅手機，仲要賣二千蚊左右包手機上網兩年月費！買咗佢，簡直更能突顯你高登仔嘅身份象徵！你係咪好想搶番部？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://timg.eprice.com.hk/hk/mobile/img/2018-08/14/211211/prince1025_1_3ab6eed7ad922ee18812e737cee63614.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftimg.eprice.com.hk%2Fhk%2Fmobile%2Fimg%2F2018-08%2F14%2F211211%2Fprince1025_1_3ab6eed7ad922ee18812e737cee63614.jpg&h=70a76903&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://timg.eprice.com.hk/hk/mobile/img/2018-08/14/211211/prince1025_1_d67df436d052c75eb86bd22fc921fcfe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftimg.eprice.com.hk%2Fhk%2Fmobile%2Fimg%2F2018-08%2F14%2F211211%2Fprince1025_1_d67df436d052c75eb86bd22fc921fcfe.jpg&h=02e0b131&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ouZENkVvKYM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FouZENkVvKYM&d=pA37NK4D6xUPDCHRwULZb5ZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=3da3a8ce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ouZENkVvKYM</a><br />\n<br />\n001：高登機係乜？實際型號係 NUU M18！NUU 好架勢，幾年前已有科技大網大力推介，係傳奇香港品牌！用呢部機，仲可以享受到最「新」嘅規格！例如 MTK 四核 CPU，2GB RAM 同八百萬像素鏡頭！iPhone 都要行埋一邊。<br />\n<br />\n002：行全宇宙最新作業系統：Anroid 7.0！係 Anroid 7.0 唔係 Android 喎！<br />\n<br />\n003：抵到想死啦！Video 裡面講明，呢部機只係賣 HK$2352。呢個價錢，仲大送 4.5G 上網，兩年上網加通話連全套增值服務，每月首 5GB 全速，過咗 5GB 限速 384kbps 無限上網。版主計過，平均計返每月都係 $98 (連行政費)，正啦喂！<br />\n<br />\n004：「網絡由中移動網絡提供」，版主唔知香港有間網絡商叫「中移動」，大部份呢 D 推銷文都用正名，咁我當佢用「中國移動香港」啦！by the way，中國移動喎，乜唔係高登仔最怕嘅中國網絡商？咁可能佢其實用數碼通你唔知呢，反正寫到唔清唔楚。<br />\n<br />\n005：用得高登機，就唔會再用 iPhone 架啦，所以佢有一個好貼心嘅功能：只能收，不能發短訊 SMS，即係九月你要抽 iPhone，就唔可以用呢個號碼去做造 iPhone 排隊嘅認證，你個心想買 iPhone 都唔比你買，你話幾貼心呢！"},{"pid":"faa46052a7dde0472646fc7dd75f80015ea996b6","tid":782924,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T07:10:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.eprice.com.hk/mobile/talk/4247/211211/1/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eprice.com.hk%2Fmobile%2Ftalk%2F4247%2F211211%2F1%2F&d=pA37NK4D6xUPDCHRwULZb5ZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=c6c4dd64\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.eprice.com.hk/mobile/talk/4247/211211/1/</a>"},{"pid":"47793f3db19ec6854aacae6444c54bd01a2df5b4","tid":782924,"uid":37733,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T07:12:19.000Z","msg":"why背面唔用小丑神"},{"pid":"4754ca4ce294d22fddc115f259f7d627bf3ecb6b","tid":782924,"uid":25424,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T07:16:49.000Z","msg":"MTK既CPU<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n又出件電子垃圾"},{"pid":"d8f95e4fb4cc33c774d3567316683a848197df70","tid":782924,"uid":22675,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T07:18:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://m.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=6943891\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Fmessage%3D6943891&d=pA37NK4D6xUPDCHRwULZb5ZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=d507dd53\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://m.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=6943891</a><br />\n真心講，Joe仔，你知唔知高登機衰咩?<br />\n係隻雞！好地地加隻雞落去做乜?<br />\n又代表唔到高登，<br />\n絲打用實比人串係雞，唔用<br />\n巴打用實比人串係小學雞，唔用<br />\n<br />\ndesign條友食左幾多忽得先諗到用隻雞代表高登?<br />\n<br />\n所以話，呢部野唔好講話大賣，有無一部銷量都成問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c711cce9050e42bfcc794a02b875f4c551e05ba2","tid":782924,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T07:18:34.000Z","msg":"有邊個會帶出街<img src=\"/asse